class PieceWiseHazard[source]

PieceWiseHazard(breakpoints, widths, **kwargs) :: Module

Piecewise Hazard where the hazard is constant between breakpoints. parameters:

  • breakpoints: time points where hazard would change
  • max_t: maximum point of time to plot to.
